  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dba 72\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three people, including Wasantha Mudalige, are interrogated for 72 hours",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police have allowed the police to detain and interrogate three people, including the convener of the Inter-University Student Union, Wasantha Mudalige, for a period of 72 hours.",
        "According to the powers assigned to a Superintendent of Police under the Prevention of Terrorism Act, they are to be detained and interrogated for a period of 72 hours.",
        "The police arrested 16 people, including Wasantha Mudalige, during a rally held by the Inter-University Student Union against the government on the 18th.",
        "The police said that after the 16 arrested suspects were presented to the court, 15 were ordered to be released on bail and one person was remanded in custody.",
        "Among the 15 released on bail, three have been detained and allowed to be interrogated."
      ],
